      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TAX DEBT (7) produced a moderate performance last time when sixth at this track over 390m behind Dodgem Duke (22.51) in a Maiden. Was in the money the start prior. Solid beginner and with a good start should have clear running out wide. Better than last start and worth following up. SHORTBREAD CINDY (4) missed the frame last time when fourth (22.30) at this track but prior to that had three placings in a row. Safe beginner but has a tricky box to overcome. Shapes as one to consider. CREEPING COLBY (6) turned in a moderate performance last time when seventh at this track over 390m behind Dodgem Duke (22.54) in a Maiden. Placed at his previous run. Speedy beginner who can find the front despite the tricky draw. Can do much better this time. OLIVER BUCK (1) is a David Sloan-trained newcomer by Bernardo out of Double 'Em Up. Drawn favourably and can capitalise. Can sneak into the frame at his first appearance.",
